- When a character reaches 0 HP, they will faint.
- A fainted character cannot interact until revived
- Revival will happen at either the next floor, or the next checkpoint
- Some items can revive a fainted comrade
- If all players faint, then they either restart the dungeon, or all revive at the previous checkpoint/rope hole. 
- Checkpoints may happen every 5 floors or so.
- Player will lose any inventory they collect on that floor if they faint. They may collect it if they revive on that floor.
